metadata.name: Urtarrila
metadata.description:
In Euskera (Basque language) the month of January (urtarrila) means "new year month".

The photo was taken in the Navarrese Pyrenees after a heavy snowfall that left me isolated for 3 days because the heavy snowfall did not allow the snow plows to clear the road. Even so, I used this time to discover new places in the area and enjoy nature alone.
